#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</title>"
msgstr "<title>Autobeskær Fjern indre kant</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This automatically removes the border of an image or selection. Use Autocrop "
"if you have a figure that does not fill the entire image or selection and "
"you wish to remove the excess whitespace. To use this feature with a "
"dithered image border, you will also need to use <link linkend=\"color-box"
"\">Color Similarity</link>."
msgstr ""
"Dette fjerner automatisk kanten af et billede eller markering. Brug "
"Autobeskær hvis du har en figur der ikke fylder hele billedet eller en "
"markering og du ønsker at fjerne ekstra hvid plads. For at bruge denne "
"funktion billede med en dithered billedkant, vil du også skulle bruge <link "
"linkend=\"color-box\">Farvelighed</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Balance</title>"
msgstr "<title>Balance</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1116 index.docbook:1154 index.docbook:1174 index.docbook:1200
#: index.docbook:1234 index.docbook:1387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is accessible from the <link linkend=\"image-more-effects"
"\">More Effects</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Der er adgang til denne funktion fra dialogen <link linkend=\"image-more-"
"effects\">Flere effekter</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to set the brightness, contrast and gamma of the image or "
"selection."
msgstr ""
"Dette tillader dig at indstille lysstyrke, kontrast og gamma for billedet "
"eller det markerede."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The more common measure of gamma (a decimal from 0.10 to 10.00) is located "
"between the <guilabel>Gamma</guilabel> spinbox and the <guibutton>Reset</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Det mere almindelige mål for gamma (et decimaltal fra 0.10 til 10.00) er "
"placeret mellem <guilabel>Gamma</guilabel> spinfeltet og <guibutton>Nulstil</"
"guibutton>-knappen."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Clear</title>"
msgstr "<title>Ryd</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid "This fills the entire image or selection with the background color."
msgstr "Dette udfylder hele billedet eller markeringen med baggrundsfarven."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on the <link linkend=\"tool-eraser-std\">Eraser</link> icon to "
"clear the entire image."
msgstr ""
"Dobbeltklik på <link linkend=\"tool-eraser-std\">Viskelæder</link>-ikonen "
"for at  rydde hele billedet."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Emboss</title>"
msgstr "<title>Præg i relief</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> to apply the Emboss effect. This "
"emphasises the edges and gives the image or selection an &quot;engraved "
"look&quot;."
msgstr ""
"Afkryds <guilabel>Aktivér</guilabel> for at anvende relief-effekt. Dette "
"lægger vægt på kanterne og giver billedet eller det markerede et &quot;"
"graveret udseende&quot;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Flatten</title>"
msgstr "<title>Flad ud</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "This recolors the image with varying shades of the two selected colors."
msgstr ""
"dette farver billedet om med varierende skygger af de to valgte farver."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1191
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<title>Flip</title>"
msgid "<title>Flip (upside down)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Flip</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1193
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "This flips the entire image or selection horizontally or vertically."
msgid "This flips the entire image or selection vertically."
msgstr "Dette flipper hele billedet eller markeringen vandret eller lodret."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Invert</title>"
msgstr "<title>Invertér</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to invert one or more RGB channels in the image or "
"selection. Select <guilabel>All</guilabel> to change a photo into a negative "
"and vice versa. This generally looks quite funny."
msgstr ""
"Dette tillader dig at invertere en eller flere RGB-kanaler i billedet eller "
"det markerede. Vælg <guilabel>Alt</guilabel> for at ændre et billede til et "
"negativ eller omvendt. Dette ser generelt ret morsomt ud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1214
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To quickly invert all channels, you do not need to use this dialog. You "
#| "can instead access the <guimenuitem>Invert Colors</guimenuitem> item in "
#| "the <guimenu>Image</guimenu> or <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> menu."
msgid ""
"To quickly invert all channels, you do not need to use this dialog. You can "
"instead access the <guimenuitem>Invert Colors</guimenuitem> item in the "
"<guimenu>Image</guimenu> or <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> menu. The "
"<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> item is only displayed in the menubar if you "
"use one of the selection tools. Additionally you can reach this action from "
"the context menu opened with a &RMB; click in the image area."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du hurtigt vil invertere alle kanaler, behøver du ikke at bruge denne "
"dialog. Du kan i stedet for gå til punktet <guimenuitem>Invertér farver</"
"guimenuitem> i menuen <guimenu>Billede</guimenu> eller <guimenu>Udvalg</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1225
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<title>Tools</title>"
msgid "<title>Mirror (horizontally)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Værktøjer</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "This flips the entire image or selection horizontally or vertically."
msgid "This mirrors the entire image or selection horizontally."
msgstr "Dette flipper hele billedet eller markeringen vandret eller lodret."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce Colors</title>"
msgstr "<title>Reducér farver</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This reduces the number of colors used by the image or selection, with or "
"without dithering."
msgstr ""
"Dette reducerer antal farver som bruges af billedet eller markeringen, med "
"eller uden gitter."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1249
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Dithering generally provides better quality results, however, you may "
#| "wish to disable it for artistic effects; <abbrev>e.g.</abbrev> using "
#| "<guilabel>Monochrome</guilabel> instead of <guilabel>Monochrome "
#| "(Dithered)</guilabel> gives a silhouette effect."
msgid ""
"Dithering generally provides better quality results, however, you may wish "
"to disable it for artistic effects; &eg; using <guilabel>Monochrome</"
"guilabel> instead of <guilabel>Monochrome (Dithered)</guilabel> gives a "
"silhouette effect."
msgstr ""
"At bruge dithering giver resultater med bedre kvalitet, men måske vil du "
"lade være med at bruge det til kunstneriske effekter, <abbrev>f.eks.</"
"abbrev> giver brug af <guilabel>Sorthvid</guilabel> i stedet for "
"<guilabel>Sorthvid (med dithering)</guilabel> en silhueteffekt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another important distinction is that while <guilabel>Monochrome (Dithered)</"
"guilabel> will always reduce the entire image or selection to black and "
"white, <guilabel>Monochrome</guilabel> will do this only if the image or "
"selection contains more than 2 colors."
msgstr ""
"En anden vigtig forskel er at mens <guilabel>Sorthvid (med dithering)</"
"guilabel> altid reducerer hele billedet eller markeringen til sorthvid, gør "
"<guilabel>Sorthvid</guilabel> det ku hvis billedet eller markeringen "
"indeholder mere end to farver."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1260
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For a quick, dithered monochrome image or selection, use the <link "
#| "linkend=\"image-monochrome\">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</link> item "
#| "of the <guimenu>Image</guimenu> or <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> menu."
msgid ""
"For a quick, dithered monochrome image or selection, use the <link linkend="
"\"image-monochrome\">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</link> item of the "
"<guimenu>Image</guimenu> or <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> menu. The "
"<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> item is only displayed in the menubar if you "
"use one of the selection tools. Additionally you can reach this action from "
"the context menu opened with a &RMB; click in the image area."
msgstr ""
"For hurtigt at få et dithered monokromt billede eller markering, bruges "
"<link linkend=\"image-monochrome\">Reducér til monokrom (Dithered)</link>-"
"punktet i <guimenu>Billede</guimenu>- eller <guimenu>Udvalg</guimenu>-menuen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the number of colors here has no effect on the color depth of the "
"file format. If you want to change the color depth, you should select it in "
"the file saving dialogs. Note that, confusingly, changing the color depth "
"also changes the number of colors."
msgstr ""
"Ændring af antallet af farver her har ingen virkning på farvedybden for "
"filformatet. Hvis du ønsker at ændre farvedybden, skal du vælge dette i "
"dialogerne til at gemme filen. Bemærk at ændring af farvedybe, noget "
"forvirrende, også ændrer antallet af farver."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce to Grayscale</title>"
msgstr "<title>Reducér til gråskala</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid "This reduces the entire image or selection to grayscale."
msgstr "Dette reducerer hele billedet eller markeringen til gråskala."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Reducér til monokrom (Dithered)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid "This reduces the entire image or selection to black and white."
msgstr "Dette reducerer hele billedet eller markeringen til sort og hvidt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want the image or selection to be dithered, use the <link "
"linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\"> Reduce Colors</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke ønsker at billedet eller det markerede skal være dithered, så "
"brug dialogen <link linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\"> Reducér farver</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Resize / Scale</title>"
msgstr "<title>Ændr størrelse / Skalér</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resizing the image changes the dimensions of the image without applying a "
"transformation to the existing contents. Scaling the image will stretch the "
"existing contents to the new dimensions. <guibutton>Smooth Scale</guibutton> "
"generally provides better quality results than Scaling, by blending "
"neighbouring colors."
msgstr ""
"Ændring af billedets størrelse ændrer dimensionerne på billedet uden at "
"anvende en  transformation på det eksisterende indhold. Skalering af "
"billedet vil strække det  eksisterende indhold til de nye dimensioner. "
"<guibutton>Glat skalering</guibutton> giver generelt bedre kvalitet end "
"skalering, ved at blande nabofarver."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can express the new dimensions in pixels, or as a percentage of the "
"original size. If you select <guilabel>Keep aspect ratio</guilabel>, the "
"width and height will be scaled by the same percentage."
msgstr ""
"Du kan udtrykke de nye dimensioner i pixels, eller som en procent af den "
"originale størrelse. Hvis du vælger <guilabel>Behold aspektratio</guilabel>, "
"vil bredden og højden blive skaleret med den samme procent."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can free-form <guibutton>Resize</guibutton> the entire image or "
"<guibutton>Smooth Scale</guibutton> the selection using the corresponding "
"handles."
msgstr ""
"Du kan frit <guibutton>ændre størrelse</guibutton> på hele billedet eller "
"bruge <guibutton>glat skalering</guibutton> af markeringen med tilsvarende "
"håndtag."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only scaling is supported for selections, and only resizing is supported for "
"text boxes. See <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Notes</link> for additional "
"details about applying these effects."
msgstr ""
"Kun skalering er understættet for markeringer, og kun ændring af størrelse "
"er understøttet for tekstfelter. Se <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Noter</"
"link> for yderligere detaljer om at anvende disse effekter."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Rotate</title>"
msgstr "<title>Rotér</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This rotates the image. You can specify the angle and direction of rotation."
msgstr ""
"Dette roterer billedet. Du kan angive vinklen og retningen af rotationen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reverse the direction of rotation by specifying a negative custom "
"angle."
msgstr ""
"Du kan vende retningen af rotation om ved at angive en negativ selvvalgt "
"vinkel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348 index.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Notes</link> for details about applying "
"this effect to a selection."
msgstr ""
"Se <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Noter</link> for detaljer om at anvende  "
"denne effekt på en markering."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1355
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Set as Image (Crop)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Sæt som billede (beskær)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will set the selection as the image."
msgstr "Dette gør markeringen til hele billedet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1360
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is only available when you have an active selection."
msgstr "Dette er kun tilgængeligt når du har en aktiv markering."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Skew</title>"
msgstr "<title>Gør skæv</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This skews the entire image or selection horizontally and/or vertically."
msgstr ""
"Dette gør hele billedet skævt eller markeringen vandret og/eller  lodret."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Soften &amp; Sharpen</title>"
msgstr "<title>Blødgør &amp; Skærp</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use this effect to soften or sharpen the image."
msgstr "brug denne effekt til at blødgøre elle skærpe billedet."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>More Effects</title>"
msgstr "<title>Flere effekter</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog contains the <link linkend=\"image-balance\">Balance</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Emboss</link>, <link linkend=\"image-flatten"
"\">Flatten</link>, <link linkend=\"image-invert\">Invert</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Reduce Colors</link> and <link linkend="
"\"image-soften-sharpen\">Soften &amp; Sharpen</link> features."
msgstr ""
"Denne dialog indeholder funktionerne <link linkend=\"image-balance"
"\">Balance</link>, <link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Præg i relief</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"image-flatten\">Flad ud</link>, <link linkend=\"image-invert"
"\">Invertér</link>, <link linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Reducér farver</"
"link> og <link linkend=\"image-soften-sharpen\">Blødgør &amp; skærp</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Notes</title>"
msgstr "<title>Noter</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resizing / Scaling</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"image-rotate\">Rotating</link> and <link linkend=\"image-skew"
"\">Skewing</link> may change the dimensions of the image. You can view the "
"new dimensions in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Ændre størrelse / skalering</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"image-rotate\">Rotere</link> og <link linkend=\"image-skew"
"\">Gør skæv</link> kan ændre dimensionerne på billedet. Du kan vise de nye "
"dimensioner i dialogen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you apply these effects to an image, the image will be resized if "
"necessary. However, if you apply these effects to a selection, the image "
"will not be resized, even if the transformed selection does not fit."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du anvender disse effekter på et billede vil billedet få ændret "
"størrelse om nødvendigt. Hvis du imidlertid anvender disse effekter på en "
"markering, vil billedets størrelse ikke blive ændret, også selvom den "
"transformerede markering ikke passer ind."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left image has been rotated 30 degrees clockwise to form the right "
"image. &kolourpaint; has automatically enlarged the image to accommodate the "
"larger contents."
msgstr ""
"Billedet til venstre  er blevet roteret 30 grader med uret for at lave "
"billedet til højre. &kolourpaint; har automatisk forstørret billedet til at "
"passe med det større indhold."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left <emphasis>selection</emphasis> has been rotated 30 degrees "
"clockwise to form the right selection. The image size has remained the same, "
"hence parts of the selection will not be visible without <link linkend="
"\"image-resize-scale\">Resizing</link> the <emphasis>image</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Det <emphasis>markerede</emphasis> til venstre er blevet roteret 30 grader "
"med uret til at lave det markerede til højre. Billedets størrelse er "
"forblevet det samme, følgelig vil dele af markeringen ikke være synlig uden "
"at <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Ændre størrelse </link> af "
"<emphasis>billedet</emphasis>."

